xfdesktop - Xfce Desktop Manager

Xfdesktop is a desktop manager for the Xfce Desktop Environment. It
handles the following tasks:

- background image / color
- root menu, window list
- minimized app icons
- file icons on the desktop (using Thunar libs)

It can bring up an applications menu and a list of all running
applications when you click on the desktop with the right or middle
mouse button respectively. Settings are available via the Settings
Manager.
